title: Weightloss Q&A
itunes:title: Weightloss Q&A
description:
We have a special treat for you. This week's podcast comes straight from inside the No BS Weightloss Program.

Each week I do a Q&A for my members. This week's questions include what to do with leftover food on your plate, why you sometimes feel shitty all day, and overeating in the CAR.

Listen in to get a taste of my teaching and preaching inside the No BS Program. You don't want to miss it.
